summary: Broke: Peter only used reading glasses, that’s why he never bothered replacing them after Flash broke them. Woke: that’s the...
body:
Broke: Peter only used reading glasses, that’s why he never bothered replacing them after Flash broke them.

Woke: that’s the shitty excuse Peter gave his friends after they asked whether he was using contact lenses and he unthinkingly said no.
